OL,4,Cshaking her baby to death
OL,6,FA mother who killed her four-month-old
OL,7,Fbaby girl by violently shaking her has
OL,8,Fbeen jailed for 15 years.
OL,10,FMelissa Wilband, 28, was found guilty
OL,11,Fby a jury of the manslaughter of Lexi
OL,12,FWilband, who collapsed at their home
OL,13,Fin Newent, Gloucestershire, in April
OL,14,F2020.
OL,16,FBristol Crown Court heard tests
OL,17,Frevealed how Lexi died following
OL,18,Fbleeding on her brain, likely caused
OL,19,Fby being violently shaken, both
OL,20,Frecently and on at least one earlier
OL,21,Foccasion.
