OL,6,FLexi died at Bristol Children's
OL,7,FHospital, with a nurse holding her
OL,8,Fhand, on 18 April ` six days after her
OL,9,Fcollapse.
OL,11,FWilband's former partner, Jack
OL,12,FWheeler, 31, was acquitted of causing
OL,13,For allowing Lexi's death.
OL,15,FMr Wheeler had also been charged with
OL,16,FLexi's manslaughter but this was
OL,17,Fformally withdrawn during the trial
OL,18,Fafter prosecutors offered no evidence
OL,19,Fagainst him.
