OL,4,Cshaking her baby to death
OL,6,F'It is hard to imagine the pain that
OL,7,FLexi must have suffered', says judge
OL,9,FPassing sentence, Mr Justice Saini
OL,10,Fsaid he was satisfied Wilband had
OL,11,Fshaken Lexi twice.
OL,13,F"Lexi was about four-months-old when
OL,14,Fshe died. She was a healthy baby," he
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,F"It is important that we recognise
OL,18,Fthis is about her life being taken.
OL,19,FYou killed Lexi by violently shaking
OL,20,Fher at the family home in Newent.
