OL,6,F"It is hard to imagine the pain that
OL,7,FLexi must have suffered both from the
OL,8,Fpast violence and the violence that
OL,9,Fled to her death. She would have cried
OL,10,Fout in anguish."
OL,12,FDetective Inspector Adam Stacey on
OL,13,FMelissa Wilband's 'self-interested
OL,14,Flies'
OL,16,FDuring the trial, jurors were told
OL,17,Fthat Wilband and Mr Wheeler were in a
OL,18,Frelationship for about three years,
OL,19,Fbut Lexi was conceived with another
OL,20,Fman in early 2019.
