OL,6,FHowever, Wilband told Mr Wheeler, of
OL,7,FLedbury, Herefordshire, that he was
OL,8,Fthe baby's biological father and
OL,9,Fpresented him with a fake DNA
OL,10,Fcertificate that claimed he was "100%"
OL,11,Fthe "farther" of her then-unborn child.
OL,13,FA genuine DNA test after Lexi's birth
OL,14,Fin November 2019 confirmed that Mr
OL,15,FWheeler was not biologically related
OL,16,Fto her, but he remained with Wilband
OL,17,Fand brought up Lexi as if she were his
OL,18,Fown child.
OL,20,FMelissa Wilband 'took cocaine' six
OL,21,Fdays after her baby was born
