OL,6,FJurors heard how Wilband, who had a
OL,7,Fvolatile relationship with Mr Wheeler,
OL,8,Ftook cocaine just six days after Lexi
OL,9,Fwas born.
OL,11,FOn April 12 2020, Wilband made a 111
OL,12,Fcall from the new-build council house
OL,13,Fwhere she lived with Mr Wheeler and
OL,14,FLexi. She claimed Lexi had stopped
OL,15,Fbreathing while in her bouncer chair.
OL,17,FLexi was taken to Gloucestershire
OL,18,FRoyal Hospital and was intubated, with
OL,19,FWilband asked if she would like to
OL,20,Fhold her baby before the procedure
OL,21,Ftook place. She declined to do so.
