OL,4,Cshaking her baby to death
OL,6,FThe infant was then transferred to
OL,7,FBristol Children's Hospital, where
OL,8,FWilband told medics that Mr Wheeler
OL,9,Fhad been carrying Lexi in her bouncer
OL,10,Fchair and was swinging it.
OL,12,FA decision was made to switch off
OL,13,FLexi's ventilator on 17 April,
OL,14,Ffollowing the results of an MRI scan.
OL,16,FNurse 'holds baby Lexi's hand through
OL,17,Fthe night' while her mother sleeps in
OL,18,Fa different part of hospital
