OL,6,FJurors were told that Wilband spent
OL,7,Fthree hours with Lexi that evening
OL,8,Fbefore leaving to go to sleep in a
OL,9,Fdifferent part of the hospital.
OL,11,FJane Osborne KC, prosecuting, said
OL,12,FWilband was aware that her baby might
OL,13,Fdie through the night but did not stay
OL,14,Fat her bedside.
OL,16,F"A staff nurse held Lexi's hand
OL,17,Fthrough the night and remained with
OL,18,Fher," Ms Osborne said.
