OL,6,FFurther tests found the areas of
OL,7,Fbleeding in Lexi's eyes were "too
OL,8,Fnumerous to count", she added.
OL,10,FGiving evidence, Wilband denied ever
OL,11,Fshaking Lexi and said she had a "bad
OL,12,Fwrist" that meant she was physically
OL,13,Funable to shake her, and sought to
OL,14,Fblame her partner.
OL,16,FMr Wheeler said he had no idea why
OL,17,FLexi had collapsed and denied carrying
